TY  - JOUR
T1  - Optimal Bandwidth Selection in Heteroskedasticity–Autocorrelation Robust Testing
AU  - Sun, Yixiao
AU  - Phillips, Peter C. B.
AU  - Jin, Sainan
Y1  - 2008/01/01
PY  - 2008
DA  - 2008/01/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.0012-9682.2008.00822.x
